					"name": "Acid Spray",
					"entries": [
						"{@atk rw} {@hit 6} to hit, range 15 ft., one target. {@h}14 ({@damage 2d10 + 3}) acid damage. The target must make a successful {@dc 13} Dexterity saving throw or fall {@condition prone} in the slick oil, which covers an area 5 feet square. A creature that enters the oily area or ends its turn there must also make the Dexterity saving throw to avoid falling {@condition prone}. A creature needs to make only one saving throw per 5-foot-square per turn, even if it enters and ends its turn in the area. The slippery effect lasts for 3 rounds."
					]
