									"type": "item",
									"name": "Stellar Flare Breath",
									"entry": "The dragon exhales star fire in a 15-foot cone. Each creature in that area must make a {@dc 13} Dexterity saving throw, taking 10 ({@damage 3d6}) fire damage and 10 ({@damage 3d6}) radiant damage on a failed save, or half as much damage on a successful one."
