									"type": "item",
									"name": "Stellar Flare Breath",
									"entry": "The dragon exhales star fire in a 30-foot cone. Each creature in that area must make a {@dc 17} Dexterity saving throw, taking 28 ({@damage 8d6}) fire damage and 28 ({@damage 8d6}) radiant damage on a failed save, or half as much damage on a successful one."
